00:37:05,220 --> 00:37:07,100
We're back to normal by Christmas, Alison,

668
00:37:07,100 --> 00:37:07,700
don't you remember?

669
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:11,640
And we'll play football against the Germans on Christmas Day.

