00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:14,880
I've just been struck dumb by that thought.

671
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:15,600
That's so good.

672
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:19,840
Sorry to anyone who does come to us for escapism

673
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:24,000
for the sudden and unprovoked mention of Boris Johnson,

