00:38:18,380 --> 00:38:23,480
I don't think we've got time to go through it in quite the detail of our previous episode,

691
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:24,580
in which we talked about Hugos.

692
00:38:24,580 --> 00:38:28,440
I've read the Hugo finalists for best novel,

693
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:31,080
with the exception of The Light Brigade,

694
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:32,900
which is the last one on my list.

695
00:38:32,900 --> 00:38:33,960
I haven't quite got to it yet,

