00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:28,940
I liked it, but it didn't quite do what Charlie Jane Anders' previous novel did for me.

717
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:30,440
Quite like Middlegame.

718
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:34,360
Really liked Memory Called Empire and The Ten Thousand Doors of January,

719
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:37,040
both of which I thoroughly enjoyed and thought were really, really good.

